Maybe this is not possible at this stage. The authors detailed the hyperparameters values of the neural network, of the method, and the initialization of the image, which is very important. However, were  several runs make ? Or was the initialization of the neural network weights fixed ? About the PET simulation, some simulation setup is missing, like the system matrix modelling, the number of line of responses.
